This Sunday, pull out all the stops for your family or guests with this home inspired flamed grilled barbecue pork ribs with onion rings.  Consuming all these carbs will be worth it as this juicy barbecue ribs dish is a recipe by popular food creator and chef Zanele van Zyl known for her social media account pages, Cooking with Zanele.   The recipe calls for a certain spice but barbecue or grilled meat seasonings would be great substitutes as well.   If you would like to make this recipe as part of your Sunday lunch feast, you can add a side of green salad, seven colours rice, fresh bread or oven-baked chips.  Instructions ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Marmalade baked sausages with a scrumptious pea salad Instructions This recipe was found on the CookingwithZanele Facebook page.